   836	## Examples
   837	
   838	> The examples in this section focus on state definitions, transitions, and
   839	> callback wiring. For readability they omit the top-level `profiles` and
   840	> `node_policy` blocks that a complete state machine YAML must declare. See
   841	> the [States Specification](rhei-states.spec.md#profiles) for the full
   842	> profile and node-policy model and the
   843	> [reference machine](states.yaml) for a complete example.
